---
// Dress code section
---

<section id="dresscode" class="section-photo py-20 px-6" style="background-image: url('/xv-jimena/images/bg/cable-car.jpg');">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-2">Código de Vestimenta</h2>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-white/40"></span>
      <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">✧</span>
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-white/40"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-card inline-block px-8 py-6">
      <p class="text-2xl text-white font-semibold mb-3">Formal / Elegante</p>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-sm max-w-md">
        Te pedimos vestir de manera formal para esta ocasión tan especial.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Color palette -->
    <div class="mt-10">
      <p class="text-white/50 font-[Montserrat] text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Paleta sugerida</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#0c8ce9] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Azul"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#3aacff] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Azul cielo"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#c0c0c0] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Plata"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#e8e8e8] border-2 border-white/50 shadow-md" title="Blanco perla"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-6 text-white/40 text-sm italic">
      ✧ Se solicita amablemente no vestir de blanco ni azul cielo ✧
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
